name: MASK [RARE]
description:
About : 

This character is made with the characteristic of wearing a mask because in 2050 in their home world, planet MXY, there are many diseases that are spreading everywhere and because of that then the leader of the planet ordered the inhabitants of planet MXY to wear masks as a characteristic and also to avoid  disease that afflicts them.

and also in 2055 where suddenly everyone has the power of the masks they wear, this is just the beginning of the war between the fellow inhabitants of the planet MXY!!!

Due to that every year there be a selection of who is most worthy of leader of PLANET MXY with tournament known as BATTLE OF MXY the participants consist of various locations of the MXY planet.
